      In order to play a QR ScanTrak game, you need to provide us with the Game ID, and optionally a password. You can get this from a game administrator or any tags that you find.<br /><br />

      <%= render 'games/joinAGame' %>

    </div>

  <% else %>

    <% if not current_user.currentGame().nil? %>

      <div id="gameInfo">


        <% #The following query finds out whether I am in a team, which belongs to my game %>
